OL,4,G2000FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,5,     GThe Allies attempt to push the
OL,6,     GGermans back to the Rhine,
OL,7,     Glaunching the largest proposed
OL,8,     Gairborne operation of WWII -
OL,9,     G30,000 paratroopers - and it goes
OL,10,     Gdisastrously wrong.
OL,11,G2030FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,12,     GIn 1944, American forces launched
OL,13,     Ga final push to retake the
OL,14,     GPhilippines after two years of
OL,15,     GJapanese occupation.
OL,16,G2100FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,17,     GJuly 1943. The German advance has
OL,18,     Gstalled, but Hitler is convinced
OL,19,     Ghis new generation of tanks will
OL,20,     Gput the Reich back on the path to
OL,21,     Gdomination. His target: the
OL,22,     GSoviet town of Kursk.
